{"tid":1202484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊撚個咁得閒搞鳩唯唯","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T09:24:41.000Z","uid":104782,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2a448d4f4f7072907eb8fb1f3121eb276eaff0","tid":1202484,"uid":104782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"作為唯唯粉絲，我想講：<br />\n咪撚玩啦<br />\n香港咁撚多親中藝人，好搞唔搞搞唯唯一個？<br />\n唯唯又唔係特別紅，要搞點解唔搞王祖藍果啲？<br />\n搞鳩唯唯根本無著數<br />\n<br />\n不過，其實唯唯有去咪大方出黎承認囉<br />\n去遊行又唔係咩大罪，咁香港人係有遊行集會嘅自由㗎嘛<br />\n本身我都好支持佢，但明明有晒證據又要喺微博否認，我對佢好失望<br />\n點解唔老實認左佢？<br />\n<br />\n唯唯，我支持你！<br />\n表態反修例，大方承認！<br />\n邊個話藝人唔可以有自己嘅政治立場？<br />\n企出黎！我哋支持你！"},{"pid":"83297dda4f8dffd146c374b52742c994aa94f80a","tid":1202484,"uid":70439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjMjhQ3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrjMjhQ3.gif&h=b32dc38d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc46302e9cd45ca492ccf8021fee8f662ab0766e","tid":1202484,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china?recruiter=554231063&amp;recruited_by_id=92a49e10-2e1d-11e6-bc11-b193dd1d0f73&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_term=address_book&amp;share_bandit_exp=message-15727601-en-GB&amp;share_bandit_var=v0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china%3Frecruiter%3D554231063%26recruited_by_id%3D92a49e10-2e1d-11e6-bc11-b193dd1d0f73%26ut